<section class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-5 py-16">
  <p class="app-eyebrow">Open source</p>
  <h1 class="mt-4 text-4xl font-semibold text-foreground">The xmode app is an AGPL-3.0 project for self-hosted software automation.</h1>
  <p class="mt-5 text-muted-foreground">This repository contains the application: workspaces, projects, issues, skills, actions, pipelines, approvals, sandboxed runs, integrations, and Change Requests. The commercial landing site and hosted-SaaS positioning are maintained in a separate private codebase.</p>
  <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
    <%= link_to "Read docs", docs_path, class: "app-btn app-btn-primary" %>
    <%= link_to "Start workspace", signup_path, class: "app-btn app-btn-muted" %>
    <% if landing_url.present? %>
      <%= link_to "Visit landing site", landing_url, class: "app-btn app-btn-muted" %>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</section>
